{"tid":1897412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟爬山","createTime":"2020-02-25T17:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T00:11:20.000Z","uid":60562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b68dfdd7997731d24c9a57aca9263cfc0983a3","tid":1897412,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"大家對爭取功能組別 呢單野<br />\n有d分歧<br />\n我就咁睇<br />\n光復香港 唔會係一時三刻既事<br />\n可以做既咪做囉<br />\n上街抗爭<br />\n遊行集會<br />\n勇武文宣<br />\n火魔裝修 <br />\n繼續做<br />\n爭取可以爭取到既所有權力<br />\n全部都要爭取<br />\n點解可以做而唔做<br />\n點解可以拎到既權力唔拎<br />\n支持所有用到既手段<br />\n今日我地未贏 我地亦都要港共難受 要佢地受苦<br />\n點解有野做而唔做<br />\n革命我都好想聽日就成功<br />\n但係革命就係要好長時間先成功<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路</span><br />\n<br />\nP.s. 希望大家熱情 唔好冷卻 好多人都冷卻左<br />\n希望快d多d集會遊行"},{"pid":"a7788b870a49b2e473ff97a2ff737707200dd44a","tid":1897412,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"7e66b89467eb48281214f323ce1f19caa053e9cc","tid":1897412,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:04:26.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"d682eb43e2171b64c52a64476b6e7d5cac6a3dd0","tid":1897412,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:04:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6222809791b476aa3cb8212425e6e7b39cd34641","tid":1897412,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"7f3de21fb593be1bee48801021d3d2e8d3c6770b","tid":1897412,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"73011ece1d924c8acf2bec8d0664dc79435f63a6","tid":1897412,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"覺得我3毛起我底"},{"pid":"e3970d0c88a55161e60abf7448f1c58a708e9642","tid":1897412,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:05: